  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Keep Syrian Children Warm this Winter</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support our efforts to provide warm clothes and blankets to the most vulnerable children in Syrian IDP camps near the borders with Turkey.  Since the beginning of the current crisis in Syria, internally displaced people (IDPs) have expressed concern about winter. Many lack warm clothes and blankets living in tent camps that are ill-prepared for cold weather. More than 200,000 IDPs living in tent camps 60% of them are children in need for assistance this winter.</narrative>
  </description>
